==English==

===Etymology===
Written form of a [[w:reduction (linguistics)|reduction]] of "[[have]] [[to]]"

===Verb phrase===
[[Category:English verbs]]
'''hafta'''
#(''colloquial'') have to; be required to
#:''I '''hafta''' fill in my tax return.''

